						               													<description>Steampunk: Wasteland Chronicles is a strategy tabletop game in the steampunk post-apocalyptic genre with detailed mechanics as well as action selection, area control, resource management and set collection. Choose one of five clans with their own unique skills. Go to the Lab for a vaccine and organize trips to the Rift for energy pods. Get weapons and resources at the Flea Market or try your luck in the Ruins or Mines. Capture the objects that will be most useful in your development! Explore technology and build steam machines!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What does a player do on their turn - the game consists of several phases. In the first phase players decide what do they do on the game board. The second phase is an action phase, when they collect their clan miniatures from the gameboard and take necessary actions. It may need dice roll, or payment, or trading, depending on chosen strategy. In the third phase, they vaccinate their clan and count points. Then the turn goes to the next player and every phase starts all over.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when either all technology cards are learned or all steam machines are built.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player with most points after all count wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
